00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:29,600
But now,

584
00:40:29,920 --> 00:40:32,120
there are no logos anymore.

585
00:40:32,720 --> 00:40:33,880
Plus,

586
00:40:34,040 --> 00:40:35,720
the timeline for drug towels

587
00:40:36,160 --> 00:40:39,000
matches what Bai Ling and Long said.

588
00:40:39,720 --> 00:40:40,600
And Xiaoguang

589
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:42,360
saw Long's car

590
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:44,680
enter Wanhuang

591
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:46,680
with the delivery trucks.

592
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:48,600
So, this place

593
00:40:48,600 --> 00:40:49,280
is definitely

594
00:40:49,280 --> 00:40:51,520
the drug towel distribution hub.

595
00:40:51,520 --> 00:40:52,480
No doubt.

596
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:55,680
But it's gone now.

597
00:40:57,320 --> 00:40:59,680
It must've happened
in those ten minutes in the parking lot.

598
00:41:07,080 --> 00:41:08,440
Don't frown.

599
00:41:09,200 --> 00:41:10,480
- Director Guan.
- Director Guan.

600
00:41:10,720 --> 00:41:11,200
Zheng Bei.

601
00:41:12,760 --> 00:41:13,640
Our Special Investigation Team

602
00:41:14,080 --> 00:41:16,160
tracked the junkie's towels
in the garbage dump

603
00:41:16,240 --> 00:41:18,080
to the pushers dumping them.

604
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:19,640
We're watching them now,

605
00:41:19,720 --> 00:41:20,960
but haven't made a move yet.

606
00:41:21,200 --> 00:41:23,520
Since this case started
in your jurisdiction,

607
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:25,600
both cities are merging the case

608
00:41:25,880 --> 00:41:27,160
under your command.

609
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:29,760
We're waiting for your lead.

610
00:41:30,080 --> 00:41:31,720
Director Guan,
you're giving us too much credit.

611
00:41:32,040 --> 00:41:33,520
We just worked well together.

612
00:41:33,520 --> 00:41:34,840
Look at Captain Wang,

613
00:41:34,840 --> 00:41:36,480
his thoughts are clear as day.

614
00:41:36,480 --> 00:41:37,960
Didn't catch the pushers

615
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:40,240
to avoid spooking the bigger fish.

616
00:41:41,920 --> 00:41:44,120
I'll leave the details to you.

617
00:41:44,720 --> 00:41:45,880
You plan it,

618
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:47,000
and we will fully cooperate.

619
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:48,000
No problem, Director Guan.

620
00:41:49,120 --> 00:41:50,080
We're family.

621
00:41:50,080 --> 00:41:51,120
Just tell us what to do.

622
00:41:51,560 --> 00:41:52,360
Sure.

623
00:41:52,440 --> 00:41:53,240
No worries, Director Guan.

624
00:41:53,240 --> 00:41:54,560
Alright, go back to work.

625
00:41:54,560 --> 00:41:55,200
Okay.

626
00:41:56,640 --> 00:41:57,440
Goodbye, Director Guan.

627
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:11,680
Any idea, Bei?

628
00:42:12,920 --> 00:42:13,760
What's the plan?

629
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:16,240
We have to catch them,

630
00:42:18,840 --> 00:42:20,200
but we need a pretext.

631
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:23,400
How are your acting skills?

632
00:42:24,640 --> 00:42:25,840
I'm solid,

633
00:42:25,840 --> 00:42:27,080
as good as Zhou Runfa.

634
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:28,720
The issue is my face

635
00:42:28,720 --> 00:42:30,760
