650
00:43:00,280 --> 00:43:01,080
Uncle?

651
00:43:01,440 --> 00:43:02,880
Which uncle?

652
00:43:03,680 --> 00:43:04,880
My master. He has retired.

653
00:43:04,880 --> 00:43:06,080
He's back on a part-time basis.

654
00:43:08,000 --> 00:43:09,200
Feels familiar.

655
00:43:09,240 --> 00:43:10,240
Very familiar.

656
00:43:11,240 --> 00:43:12,640
Alright, if Uncle's mentioned,

657
00:43:12,760 --> 00:43:14,400
today,

658
00:43:15,240 --> 00:43:16,360
why not introduce everyone

659
00:43:16,360 --> 00:43:17,920
properly today?

660
00:43:18,080 --> 00:43:19,520
- Sure, sounds good.
- Let's do it.

661
00:43:21,040 --> 00:43:23,280
Pan, forensic expert.

662
00:43:25,760 --> 00:43:26,560
Hello.

663
00:43:27,240 --> 00:43:28,920
Zhou Xi, my disciple.

664
00:43:31,400 --> 00:43:33,720
This one here feels especially familiar.

665
00:43:36,160 --> 00:43:37,840
And don't mess with her.

666
00:43:38,360 --> 00:43:39,280
Look at her build.

667
00:43:39,280 --> 00:43:40,920
She's our local Sanda champion.

668
00:43:44,040 --> 00:43:44,840
A real tough one.

669
00:43:45,040 --> 00:43:45,960
Right, Yuan?

670
00:43:46,760 --> 00:43:47,560
Low profile.

671
00:43:48,120 --> 00:43:49,360
Isn't that Yao?

672
00:43:50,360 --> 00:43:51,160
Wu Gang, Mr. Wu.

673
00:43:51,160 --> 00:43:52,920
No introduction needed.

674
00:44:22,480 --> 00:44:23,200
Over there.

675
00:44:24,320 --> 00:44:25,440
After Erjin was caught,

676
00:44:25,440 --> 00:44:26,920
Jin Fei moved here.

677
00:44:30,440 --> 00:44:31,240
Let's go.

678
00:44:58,540 --> 00:44:59,840
Drink something.

679
00:45:20,600 --> 00:45:22,080
You can't go on an empty stomach.

680
00:45:27,280 --> 00:45:29,200
That's not what I want.

681
00:45:30,600 --> 00:45:31,640
You know what I want.

682
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:36,360
Jin Fei, you shouldn't be like this.

683
00:45:36,880 --> 00:45:38,000
What should I do, then?

684
00:45:43,880 --> 00:45:45,160
You deserve a better life.

685
00:45:45,200 --> 00:45:46,320
A better life?

686
00:45:47,920 --> 00:45:48,960
Like yours?

687
00:46:11,280 --> 00:46:12,840
You like me, don't you?

688
00:46:34,680 --> 00:46:36,160
Get me some Lucifer.

689
00:46:37,680 --> 00:46:39,000
Or ecstasy,

690
00:46:40,200 --> 00:46:41,320
anything.

691
00:46:42,160 --> 00:46:43,520
Get it for me,

692
00:46:47,080 --> 00:46:48,880
and I'm yours.

693
00:46:53,360 --> 00:46:54,360
What are you doing?

694
00:46:56,000 --> 00:46:57,360
Just give me a little.

695
00:46:58,840 --> 00:47:00,000
Just a little.

696
00:47:01,160 --> 00:47:02,200
Just a little.

